// https://www.shadertoy.com/view/4clcWl three points ring, 2024 by jt
// related:
// https://www.shadertoy.com/view/lffyDs four points sphere
// https://www.shadertoy.com/view/4csyDX three points circle

// A ring through three points in space.

// tags: triangle, circle, ring, three, points, point, circum

